{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775891625474,"sessionID":"ses_2849f24e1ffeeewZ5S6mmQ6lGS","part":{"id":"prt_d7b63316e001EX1yJH5roR3UB0","messageID":"msg_d7b614c31001nsVBe1DJLU9Tdz","sessionID":"ses_2849f24e1ffeeewZ5S6mmQ6lGS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/notes.md","content":"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Notes\n\n## Development Notes\n\n### Design Decisions\n- Sync/async execution modes for flexibility\n- Configurable polling intervals for status command\n- Multiple input formats (JSON, file, key-value)\n\n### Technical Considerations\n- Use shared HTTP client from existing CLI modules\n- Follow existing error handling patterns\n- Ensure proper exit codes for scripting support\n\n### API Assumptions\n- Backend provides `/api/v1/executions` endpoints\n- Authentication handled via existing auth module\n- Execution states: pending, running, completed, failed, cancelled\n\n## Change Log\n\n### 2026-04-11\n- Initial scaffold creation\n- Created spec.yaml, delta-spec.md, design.md, plan.md, tasks.md, notes.md, tests.md\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/notes.md","time":{"start":1775891625454,"end":1775891625473}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775891625476,"sessionID":"ses_2849f24e1ffeeewZ5S6mmQ6lGS","part":{"id":"prt_d7b634c34001O4cjQe6u3EopnR","messageID":"msg_d7b614c31001nsVBe1DJLU9Tdz","sessionID":"ses_2849f24e1ffeeewZ5S6mmQ6lGS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/tests.md","content":"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Test Specification\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Execution Client Tests\n- [ ] `test_submit_execution_success` - Verify successful execution submission\n- [ ] `test_submit_execution_invalid_agent` - Handle agent not found error\n- [ ] `test_submit_execution_invalid_input` - Handle invalid input error\n- [ ] `test_get_status_pending` - Query pending execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_status_running` - Query running execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_status_completed` - Query completed execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_status_failed` - Query failed execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_result_success` - Fetch execution results\n- [ ] `test_get_result_not_ready` - Handle result not ready error\n- [ ] `test_retry_on_transient_error` - Verify retry logic\n\n### Input Parser Tests\n- [ ] `test_parse_json_string_input` - Parse JSON string inputs\n- [ ] `test_parse_key_value_input` - Parse key=value pairs\n- [ ] `test_parse_file_input` - Parse JSON file input\n- [ ] `test_parse_merged_inputs` - Merge multiple input sources\n- [ ] `test_parse_invalid_json` - Handle invalid JSON\n- [ ] `test_parse_file_not_found` - Handle missing file\n\n### Formatter Tests\n- [ ] `test_format_json_output` - Format response as JSON\n- [ ] `test_format_table_output` - Format response as table\n- [ ] `test_format_status_colors` - Apply color coding to status\n- [ ] `test_format_empty_result` - Handle empty results\n\n### Invoke Command Tests\n- [ ] `test_invoke_async_success` - Async invoke returns execution ID\n- [ ] `test_invoke_sync_success` - Sync invoke waits and returns result\n- [ ] `test_invoke_sync_timeout` - Handle sync timeout\n- [ ] `test_invoke_with_file_input` - Invoke with file input\n- [ ] `test_invoke_with_json_input` - Invoke with JSON input\n- [ ] `test_invoke_with_kv_input` - Invoke with key-value input\n- [ ] `test_invoke_agent_not_found` - Handle agent not found\n- [ ] `test_invoke_invalid_input` - Handle invalid input parameters\n\n### Status Command Tests\n- [ ] `test_status_query_success` - Query execution status\n- [ ] `test_status_not_found` - Handle execution not found\n- [ ] `test_status_watch_mode` - Test continuous polling\n- [ ] `test_status_completed_exit` - Exit code 0 when completed\n- [ ] `test_status_failed_exit` - Exit code 3 when failed\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n### Workflow Tests\n- [ ] `test_invoke_then_status` - Invoke agent and check status\n- [ ] `test_invoke_sync_full_workflow` - Complete sync workflow\n- [ ] `test_invoke_async_poll_until_complete` - Poll until completion\n\n### Error Handling Tests\n- [ ] `test_network_error_handling` - Handle network failures\n- [ ] `test_auth_error_handling` - Handle authentication failures\n- [ ] `test_server_error_handling` - Handle server errors\n\n## E2E Tests\n\n### Happy Path\n- [ ] `test_e2e_invoke_async_agent` - End-to-end async invocation\n- [ ] `test_e2e_invoke_sync_agent` - End-to-end sync invocation\n- [ ] `test_e2e_status_tracking` - Track execution status\n\n### Edge Cases\n- [ ] `test_e2e_large_input` - Handle large input payloads\n- [ ] `test_e2e_long_running` - Handle long-running executions\n- [ ] `test_e2e_concurrent_invocations` - Multiple concurrent invokes\n\n## Test Data Requirements\n\n### Mock Agent\n- Simple echo agent for testing\n- Agent with required parameters\n- Agent with optional parameters\n\n### Mock Responses\n- Pending status response\n- Running status response\n- Completed status with result\n- Failed status with error message\n"},"output":"Wrote file